ese tourist, even it isn't really<br />\n- ada wont do any m&amp;a, big boss is a bit busy right now in my view[/quote]<br />\n多謝巴打嘅建議/問題<br />\n好奇心之下都去左望望 太古廣場(PP) 幾錢 =&gt; 估唔到可以 $110-$160<br />\n<a href=\"http://oir.centanet.com/office/transaction?searchTxt=%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B41%E6%9C%9F&amp;postType=All\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foir.centanet.com%2Foffice%2Ftransaction%3FsearchTxt%3D%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B41%25E6%259C%259F%26postType%3DAll&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=344ccbfa\" target=\"_blank\">http://oir.centanet.com/office/transaction?searchTxt=%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B41%E6%9C%9F&amp;postType=All</a><br />\n題外話, 太古地產嘅寫字樓有70% 以上都要2021年或打後先到期<br />\n<br />\n再望下 3Garden 前面嘅中銀大廈(無錯, 可能比較少人知係有出租嘅)<br />\n<a href=\"https://midlandici.com.hk/ics/property/details/office/Central/Bank-of-China-Tower-High-Floor/111667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmidlandici.com.hk%2Fics%2Fproperty%2Fdetails%2Foffice%2FCentral%2FBank-of-China-Tower-High-Floor%2F111667&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=03bdef21\" target=\"_blank\">https://midlandici.com.hk/ics/property/details/office/Central/Bank-of-China-Tower-High-Floor/111667</a><br />\n$120-$160<br />\nIFC $220<br />\n對面海嘅ICC 就做緊 $100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n商務租嘅市場唔太熟, 但好似唔會同住宅一樣咁要分到咁仔細座向景觀樓層/行幾多樓梯...etc(不過老實我都懶行上ICBC tower)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終 中環就係中環, PP 係金鐘比一感覺次左一級, 加上PP 要2021年先可以再有供應, 中環甲一級至少依一年兩真係無乜選擇<br />\n望下ICC 個價就知, 又靚又新又方便, 都係會差中環一大折租金<br />\n<br />\n至於M&amp;A,  依個唔去估啦, 作為小股民, 只可以係&quot;希望&quot;佢會有新商廈<br />\n當bonus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d6759be53f351b8ffd426ef7860152f64516b2","tid":1105191,"uid":55445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"2778 係15年開始股息年年都增長<br />\n算係咁<br />\n778 愈黎愈衰<br />\n當然同reits 中之霸823 無得比<br />\n但係823 現價真係太撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603ac1add74e027fdf3e8ee1324c02faf3adad9e","tid":1105191,"uid":56765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"想買隻reit長期hold住<br />\n但唔敢而家入823 個價好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哩隻2778會唔會好選擇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d733543c850964e0b6b85edbe37d146dfc7dac7e","tid":1105191,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T08:47:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬點睇 1972<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺太古坊返工 睇住佢拆完又起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453e1d088114b53438fbea43f28373b60b01ad45","tid":1105191,"uid":10922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:14:21.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以分析下435"}]}